.TH CORTEX 1 "2026-03-23" "cortex 2.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
cortex \- Python implementation of cortex list and status commands
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cortex
[
B-h
    R | 
        B--help
               R]
.br
.B cortex

ICOMMAND
        R [
           ISUBCOMMAND
                      R] [
                          IARGS
                               R...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cortex
is Python implementation of cortex list and status commands
.SH COMMANDS
Available commands:
.TP
.B agent
Agent commands
.TP
.B rules
Rule commands
.TP
.B hooks
Hook commands
.TP
.B skills
Skill commands
.TP
.B mcp
MCP server commands
.TP
.B worktree
Git worktree management commands
.TP
.B git
Safe git operations
.TP
.B tmux
Tmux window management for agents
.TP
.B statusline
Render Claude Code status line
.TP
.B tui
Launch interactive TUI for agent management
.TP
.B ai
AI assistant commands
.TP
.B export
Export context commands
.TP
.B install
Install CLI integrations and optional extras
.TP
.B memory
Memory capture commands for persistent knowledge storage
.TP
.B plan
View and manage plan files
.TP
.B docs
Browse documentation (includes bundled package docs)
.TP
.B dev
Development and maintenance tools
.TP
.B file
Claude Files API utilities
.TP
.B uninstall
Uninstall cortex
.TP
.B status
Show overall status
.TP
.B review
Run review gate before task completion
.TP
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Show help message and exit
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT
Override for context directory (set automatically by Claude Code when running plugin commands)
.SH FILES
.TP
.B ~/.claude/
Default context directory containing agents, modes, rules, and other configuration
